   Category: Technology

   Technological advances are providing people with disabilities
   unprecedented opportunity for obtaining independence and mobility. The
   Administration will encourage businesses to give computers and Internet
   access to employees with disabilities by making it explicit that this
   provision is a tax-free benefit. New Freedom Initiative

